SUMMARY:March Music Madness - Duos
DESCRIPTION:Three duos. One night. Big March Madness energy—intimate sets\, killer chemistry\, and nonstop live music.\nMarch Madness Duos brings a full night of paired-up power to the stage\, celebrating musical chemistry and collaboration. Each set features a unique duo\, delivering stripped-down\, high-energy performances that put connection and musicianship front and center. \nThe night kicks off at 7pm with Volker Strifler and Gary Silva\, followed by Gloria Strasburg’s Equinox Duo at 8pm\, and wraps up at 9pm with Nick Otis and Matt Silva. Come for one set or stay for all three—it’s a fast-paced\, music-filled night you won’t want to miss. \nTickets $12 in advance\, $18 at the door. Doors open 6:30pm.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/march-music-madness-duos/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/MarchMadness-Duos.jpg
GEO:38.44252;-122.71621
