SUMMARY:Coffey Park at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Hailing from Santa Rosa\, Coffey Park Band is a high-energy North Bay cover band known for bringing communities together through great music and unforgettable live shows. With roots in classic rock and a setlist that spans decades\, the band delivers a dynamic mix of rock anthems\, dance favorites\, pop hits\, and crowd-pleasing sing-alongs that keep audiences on their feet. \nFormed by local musicians who share a passion for live performance\, Coffey Park Band has built a reputation for tight musicianship\, rich harmonies\, and an infectious stage presence. Their shows blend nostalgia and modern flair — seamlessly moving from timeless classics to upbeat contemporary hits — creating a soundtrack that appeals to multiple generations.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/coffey-park-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
LOCATION:Rio Nido Roadhouse\, 14540 Canyon 2 Road\, Rio Nido\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
