SUMMARY:SRJC Orchestra Concert: From Hollywood to Broadway
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for a family night of magic as the orchestra brings to life some of the most beloved music from stage and screen. \nSRJC Orchestra Concert: From Hollywood to Broadway\nGet ready for an unforgettable night with the SRJC Orchestra as they take you on a musical journey From Hollywood to Broadway! Join us for an evening filled with your favorite tunes from Wicked\, How to Train Your Dragon\, Gladiator\, The Little Mermaid\, Frozen\, The Lion King\, Moana\, Hercules and Beauty and the Beast. Whether you’re a film buff or a theater lover\, this concert has something special for everyone. Don’t miss out on this awesome live performance—bring the whole family and enjoy this magical concert.
