SUMMARY:Forbidden Kiss LIVE - Steampunk
DESCRIPTION:Don’t miss this show featuring Steampunk fashion and props – bring or wear your own!\nQu’in de la Noche makes her premiere appearance at Forbidden Kiss LIVE in this Steampunk-themed show.\nCheryl King presents bawdy vaudeville at its finest\, with burlesque from Thotty McNaughty\, and musical performances from Ruby Reprise and Karenna Slade. Titus Androgynous will bring their new drag routine\, and Underground Improv provides comedy sketches and improvisation with prompts from the audience.\nA costume contest is planned\, with the audience voting for their favorites with our voting app\, and prizes awarded!\nPURCHASE IN ADVANCE AND SAVE! PLUS RESERVE A TABLE WITH OUR ZONE TICKET OPTION\nReserved seating in Zone A $27\, Zone B $22\, Zone C $17 (does not guarantee seating) Tickets at the door $27 (seating not guaranteed).\nDoors open 6:30pm.\nAdult material. 18+\nOur kitchen serves our All New Menu from the time doors open until end of intermission. (Kitchen available only at events with 60 or more advance tickets sold)
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/forbidden-kiss-live-steampunk/
